parameters:
Looking at the bonfire somehow calms my heart... Laura's HP
and MP have been fully restored!

...So there were still survivors. It's convenient that you
came to us... it saves us some trouble...
取り巻きがラウラたちを見る

\SE[2]Who are you all? \SE[3]And why did you do something
like this?

Sorry, but we don't have names to introduce ourselves to
you... We're just here to quickly finish our job.

We're busy here too. We don't have time to chat. Sorry, but
give up on everything... and die.

...You bastards. It's time to finish this. \!Clean up
quickly.
じりじりと間合いを詰める取り巻き
ラウラ一歩後ろにたじろぎ

\SM[nod]\SE\SE[0]Don't worry. Laura, \SE[0]I said we'll take
care of all of them, right?

\SE[47]I've had many important things taken from me...
\SE[48]I'm a little angry. \SE[2]...That's why.

\SE[4]I've decided to kill all of you. \SE[0]Are you
prepared for that?
本気ルナロアが敵を20体くらいぼこすと戦闘一旦終了
やりたいこととしては
終盤の魔法ばんばん使ってショッキングな絵面と
キャラを育てた先の期待感を出したいのと
単純なキャラクターのアピール。
これ用に別キャラ用意してもいいかも
戦闘中に倒したモブは倒れたまま消えない。
延々と死体が増えていく感じに
